org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation

Class UniversalOverride

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.assignment.context.AbstractClassWithContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation.Reservation
        • org.cpsolver.studentsct.reservation.UniversalOverride
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Reservation>, AssignmentComparable<Reservation,Request,Enrollment>, CanHoldContext, CanInheritContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>, HasAssignmentContext<Request,Enrollment,Reservation.ReservationContext>

    public class UniversalOverride
extends Reservation
    Universal reservation override. A reservation override using a student filter. Student filter contains a boolean expression with the following attributes: area, classification, major, minor, group, accommodation, campus, advisor or student external id, and status. For example: major:M1 or major:M2 would match all students with majors M1 or M2.
